doc.after: China Southern Airlines serves 193 destinations in 35 different countries worldwide 41 It maintains a strong presence in the domestic market with its main hubs at Beijing Capital International Airport Guangzhou Baiyun International Airport Chongqing Jiangbei International Airport and r mqi Diwopu International Airport along with other focus cities in Changchun Changsha Dalian Shanghai Shenyang Shenzhen Wuhan and Zhengzhou The airline plans to continue to develop Chongqing and r mqi as hubs as well to exploit the domestic market potential 42
